From: Tiejun Chen <tiejun.chen@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 30 Aug 2011 18:39:27 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ppc-mc/fsl_p4080ds: Need to support irq affinity

Enable irq affinity in direct irq mode for E500mc.

Signed-off-by: Tiejun Chen <tiejun.chen@windriver.com>
---
 kernel/vbi/wrhv.c |    8 --------
 1 files changed, 0 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

diff --git a/kernel/vbi/wrhv.c b/kernel/vbi/wrhv.c
index 1d40dc8..57b97be 100644
--- a/kernel/vbi/wrhv.c
+++ b/kernel/vbi/wrhv.c
@@ -248,14 +248,6 @@ int wrhv_irq_set_affinity(unsigned int irq,
 	int cpu;
 	struct wrhv_irq_head *head = &wrhv_irq_head;
 
-	/* Currently we don't support set affinity in direct irq mode */
-	if (wrhv_dir_irq) {
-		printk(KERN_WARNING "Currently we don't support set affinity"
-			" in direct irq mode on e500mc.\n");
-
-		return -1;
-	}
-
 	if (cpumask_equal(desc->affinity, dest))
 		return 0;
 
